{"tid":2508861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：斥20億重建西區已婚警察宿舍","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:20:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea1783da0c58fd89bc6cad427cfbed2d13dc51e","tid":2508861,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"政府擬斥20億元重建西區已婚警務人員宿舍 <br />\n<br />\n政府計劃向立法會申請20.2億元，重建西區已婚警務人員宿舍，預計7年內完工，可提供540個宿舍單位。當局表示，西區警署建築群在1950年代落成，而目前警隊欠缺超過3400個宿舍單位，短缺率為22%，現時員佐級宿舍輪候時間約5年，因此建議重建，紓緩宿位短缺問題，節省舊宿舍保養維修開支。由於有高度限制，建築物只能向下發展，日後平台和地庫除了用作附屬設施外，亦會興建西區警區和警察公共關係科的設施，應付服務需要。 <br />\n<br />\n對於有區議員要求加入社區設施，當局指宿舍用地位於西區警署之內，基於保安理由和行動效率的考慮，不適宜加入社區設施。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389408&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=cdb0b0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389408</a>"},{"pid":"7616aeacc4b459fc6f4c22c0fb5bd974ac1b100c","tid":2508861,"uid":33352,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"公屋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8db18eb0ffc745bc46f940aca7ab1658271d9c9","tid":2508861,"uid":224066,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWgCdLK5WCPFtMWuFpS1eQLXPArCgpBUz6wLYf4Re9CxM?filename=fHXYpYb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHXYpYb.gif&h=2c0fa9e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b726462170edbb6a9d5ddfd3872feeba43ada851","tid":2508861,"uid":357710,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7616aeacc4b459fc6f4c22c0fb5bd974ac1b100c","tid":2508861,"uid":33352,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"公屋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim